headline: The Bull Case For IDEXX Laboratories (IDXX) Could Change Following Strong Q3 Beat And Guidance Hike - Learn Why
summary: IDEXX Laboratories recently reported third-quarter 2025 earnings per share of $3.40, up over one-fifth year over year and ahead of expectations, while raising its full-year 2025 guidance for both revenue and earnings growth. The upside was powered by strong performances in the Companion Animal Group and Livestock, Poultry and Dairy segments, highlighting the value of recurring diagnostic revenues and expanding international operations even as some investors remain watchful of debt levels and...
